- [ ] `DATABASE_URL` inserted for both production and preview scopes
- [ ] Connection string is valid and app can connect
- [ ] `deprovision()` drops database and user
- [ ] `deprovision()` removes `managed_databases` row and `env_vars` rows
- [ ] `deprovision()` terminates active connections before dropping
- [ ] `getDatabaseInfo()` returns accurate size and connection count
